<h2>What's New in 1.7.5</h2>  <strong>Bug Fixes</strong> <ul><li>Fixed false-positive "No network connection" and "Not signed in" banners that briefly appeared on every launch before the app had fully initialized</li> <li>Fixed sign-in via the Connect button unnecessarily opening a login window when your session was still valid — it now silently restores your session</li> <li>Fixed widgets retaining stale data after signing out</li>  <strong>Settings</strong> <li>Removed the "Send test notification" button</li> <li>Added "Need Help?" links to GitHub Issues and @niederme on X</li></ul>
</body>
